### 1. Get fresh Keycloak access token
POST http://localhost:8086/realms/smart-travel/protocol/openid-connect/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

client_id=smart-travel-client&username=demo-user&password=demo-pass&grant_type=password

> {%
    client.global.set("access_token", response.body.access_token);
%}


### 2. Gateway health
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/health


### 3. Trip Service health
GET http://localhost:8081/actuator/health


### 4. Recommendation Service health
GET http://localhost:8082/actuator/health


### 5. MCP Server health
GET http://localhost:8087/actuator/health


### 6. Security negative test - should return 401 without token
GET http://localhost:8080/api/trips


### 7. External API status through Gateway
GET http://localhost:8080/api/recommendations/external/status
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}


### 8. Get Paris seed recommendations through Gateway
GET http://localhost:8080/api/recommendations?destination=Paris&type=ATTRACTION
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

> {%
    if (response.body.length > 0) {
        client.global.set("recommendation_id", response.body[0].id);
    }
%}


### 9. Get Rome live recommendations through Geoapify fallback
GET http://localhost:8080/api/recommendations?destination=Rome&type=ATTRACTION
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

> {%
    if (response.body.length > 0) {
        client.global.set("live_recommendation_id", response.body[0].id);
        client.global.set("live_recommendation_source", response.body[0].source);
    }
%}


### 10. Repeat Rome live recommendations to verify no duplicate DB records
GET http://localhost:8080/api/recommendations?destination=Rome&type=ATTRACTION
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}


### 11. Get Skopje restaurants through live API or fallback
GET http://localhost:8080/api/recommendations/restaurants?destination=Skopje
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}


### 12. Get Ohrid hotels with budget through live API or fallback
GET http://localhost:8080/api/recommendations/hotels?destination=Ohrid&budget=100
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}


### 13. Get Paris attractions endpoint
GET http://localhost:8080/api/recommendations/attractions?destination=Paris
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}


### 14. Create trip through Gateway
POST http://localhost:8080/api/trips
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "demo-user",
  "destination": "Paris",
  "startDate": "2026-07-10",
  "endDate": "2026-07-15",
  "budget": 800,
  "currency": "EUR"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("trip_id", response.body.id);
%}


### 15. Get all trips through Gateway
GET http://localhost:8080/api/trips
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}


### 16. Get trips by user through Gateway
GET http://localhost:8080/api/trips?userId=demo-user
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}


### 17. Get trip by id through Gateway
GET http://localhost:8080/api/trips/{{trip_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}


### 18. Update trip status through Gateway
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/trips/{{trip_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "demo-user",
  "destination": "Paris",
  "startDate": "2026-07-10",
  "endDate": "2026-07-15",
  "budget": 800,
  "currency": "EUR",
  "status": "PLANNED"
}


### 19. Trip Service calls Recommendation Service through Feign
GET http://localhost:8080/api/trips/{{trip_id}}/recommendations
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}


### 20. Save seed recommendation to trip
POST http://localhost:8080/api/recommendations/{{recommendation_id}}/save
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tripId": {{trip_id}},
  "userId": "demo-user"
}


### 21. Save live Geoapify recommendation to trip
POST http://localhost:8080/api/recommendations/{{live_recommendation_id}}/save
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tripId": {{trip_id}},
  "userId": "demo-user"
}


### 22. Get saved recommendations for trip
GET http://localhost:8080/api/recommendations/saved?tripId={{trip_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}


### 23. Estimate trip cost through Trip Service
GET http://localhost:8080/api/trips/{{trip_id}}/estimated-cost
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}


### 24. Estimate trip cost through Recommendation Service
GET http://localhost:8080/api/recommendations/estimate?tripId={{trip_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}


### 25. MCP REST test - recommend places
GET http://localhost:8087/api/mcp-test/recommend-places?destination=Paris&type=ATTRACTION&limit=3


### 26. MCP REST test - get trip details
GET http://localhost:8087/api/mcp-test/trip/{{trip_id}}


### 27. MCP REST test - get saved attractions
GET http://localhost:8087/api/mcp-test/saved-attractions?tripId={{trip_id}}


### 28. MCP REST test - estimate trip cost
GET http://localhost:8087/api/mcp-test/estimate?tripId={{trip_id}}


### 29. Optional cleanup - delete trip at the end
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/trips/{{trip_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}